-----------------------Why This Project Matters???????????????????????????????
This Power BI dashboard was developed to address a critical need for category managers and stakeholders at Othoba. The ability to track daily sales performance is essential for making data-driven decisions regarding product campaigns, inventory management, and sales strategies.

With this dashboard, stakeholders can:
✔️ Monitor real-time sales performance across different product categories.
✔️ Identify top-performing products and vendors to optimize supply chain decisions.
✔️ Analyze sales trends and customer purchase behavior to drive targeted marketing campaigns.
✔️ Evaluate profit margins and cancellation rates to improve overall business efficiency.

By leveraging Power BI’s dynamic visualizations and Excel’s preprocessing capabilities, this project ensures that decision-makers have accurate and actionable insights at their fingertips.

